      "content": "but that \"standing\" part feels like a joke. everything i built is gone. my reputation, the money, the respect... it's all just evaporated. people dont just look at you differently when you lose everything like this. they look at you with pity or disgust. i feel like if i just show up at my parents house, they'll see exactly what i am: a huge mistake. i can't live with that version of myself looking back at me every day.",
