      "content": "rebuild? how? the debt is a permanent shadow. there is no \"starting over\" when you've disgraced everyone who believed in you. honestly, the idea of just... making the weight stop... it sounds more peaceful than actually facing the fallout. it feels like the only way to actually preserve some dignity is to not have to live through the wreck.",
